    "description": "<span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1884700/extras/1baa0a2c906863df66245ee6989e2247.avif?t=1644487466\" width=620 height=100 /></span><br>Dangerous Drift consists of two types of races: Drift and Racing.<br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>Drift: Wear out your vehicle's tires by drifting to the end.</li></ul><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>Racing: Compete against your rivals and show them who's in charge.</li></ul><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1884700/extras/23d5206a88aef6e0bb73d4ca8ab4e555.avif?t=1644487466\" width=620 height=100 /></span><br>Challenge your friends in Dangerous Drift online multiplayer, compete for victory.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1884700/extras/06eb360f6b3bef8854cb00098e2b9950.avif?t=1644487466\" width=620 height=100 /></span><br>Choose your vehicle based on the class of the race, among more than 28 different vehicles each with a unique handling.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1884700/extras/350317e56cf603f2e4a9baeab4496f9f.avif?t=1644487466\" width=620 height=100 /></span><br>Compete in dozens of different places around the world: Forests, Metropolitan Cities, Swamps, Snowy Mountains, Desert and much more.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1884700/extras/007592faaa7160ea513deca53def8337.avif?t=1644487466\" width=620 height=100 /></span><br>During races, vehicles can be damaged and body parts lost during collisions, which will hamper the passage of drivers in the next few laps.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1884700/extras/9ff37024846c05a01081ef837a7e973b.avif?t=1644487466\" width=620 height=100 /></span><br>Each race is different from the other, we will have to compete in different weather conditions (Clear, cloudy, rain, fog, snow) and times of the day (Day, night, sunrise).",
